high_descs: Pick up the knife to the left of the stove.
Put the knife in the cup on the counter in front of you.
Pick up the cup with the knife.
Turn right and head towards the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cup with a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Pick up the knife to the left of the stove.
Put the knife in the mug next to the stove.
Pick up the mug with knife in it.
Bring the mug to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle.
Place the knife tip down in the black mug on the kitchen counter.
Pick up the mug with the large metal knife in it.
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the mug with the knife in it into the kitchen sink to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a large metal knife in it into the kitchen sink.
